This package contains roles for the Magic Lantern Java2D platform.

    Class Description
    Mle2dRole
    The 2D Role base class.
    MleImageCarrier

    MleImageRole
    This class implements a Role that can display an image.

Package com.wizzer.mle.parts.roles Description

This package contains roles for the Magic Lantern Java2D platform.

The package provides a Role that may be used for rendering an image.
